{"content": "I need to multiply 470 \u00d7 a98 in base 11.\n\nFirst, let me convert to base 10 to calculate:\n- 470\u2081\u2081 = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070 = 4\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 0 = 484 + 77 = 561\u2081\u2080\n- a98\u2081\u2081 = 10\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 8\u00d711\u2070 = 10\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 8 = 1210 + 99 + 8 = 1317\u2081\u2080\n\nNow multiply:\n561 \u00d7 1317 = 738,837\u2081\u2080\n\nNow convert 738,837\u2081\u2080 to base 11:\n738,837 \u00f7 11 = 67,167 remainder 0\n67,167 \u00f7 11 = 6,106 remainder 1\n6,106 \u00f7 11 = 555 remainder 1\n555 \u00f7 11 = 50 remainder 5\n50 \u00f7 11 = 4 remainder 6\n4 \u00f7 11 = 0 remainder 4\n\nReading the remainders from bottom to top: 465110\u2081\u2081\n\nLet me verify: 4\u00d711\u2075 + 6\u00d711\u2074 + 5\u00d711\u00b3 + 1\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n= 4\u00d7161,051 + 6\u00d714,641 + 5\u00d71,331 + 1\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 0\n= 644,204 + 87,846 + 6,655 + 121 + 11\n= 738,837 \u2713\n\n465110", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 44, "completion_tokens": 462}